{"tid":2147511,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"莉法同肥豬真係天生一對！","createTime":"2020-08-09T09:45:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T17:21:24.000Z","uid":57911,"like":65,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"af70c290c07dcccdc0c462edfde325740fdc310b","tid":2147511,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T09:45:51.000Z","msg":"我從來都冇諗過會出個咁嘅post<br />\n因為莉法一早已經有雷根<br />\n雷根有幾好仔相信唔洗我講<br />\n佢係甚至可以為咗大哥(桐人)<br />\n而自爆幫佢開路嘅真男人<br />\n佢打機可以夠膽隻身隱身試探情報&hellip;<br />\n吹奏雷根嘅我就唔再講了<br />\n今次主題係肥豬<br />\n<br />\n莉法真係好有異性緣<br />\n識親嘅男仔都係真男人<br />\n既然佢有雷根點解我仲會講肥豬<br />\n因為肥豬又善良又冇機心<br />\n同莉法一撚樣<br />\n完全願意為人付出而受傷<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n更重要係佢哋個髮型都一撚樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NiU6kaz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNiU6kaz.jpg&h=6d728d64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>一撚樣係金色辮仔頭</strong></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"pink\">希望佢哋可以好似史迪加咁幸福</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11e7e7dfc9f0b7f7d19d8101eb4be80601a5e7ce","tid":2147511,"uid":158899,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T09:49:09.000Z","msg":"接受唔到 豬撚屌人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"863b0ecc7caed2a893636838e2dee2b5038336ba","tid":2147511,"uid":286199,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T09:51:24.000Z","msg":"比人插爆隻眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb7220102879df9a6c779c7eb8702034318abede","tid":2147511,"uid":175208,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"cit